\h\ #wSHUTDOWN \d\

\u\USAGE\n\
#wshutdown [message]

\u\DESCRIPTION\n\
Shut down CurryMUD, optionally with a custom message.
If you do not provide a custom message, the default message will be sent.

\u\EXAMPLES\n\
\q\"#wshutdown"\d\ to shut down CurryMUD.4`
\q\"#wshutdown We are shutting down to reboot with new bug fixes in place. Come back in 5 mins. Thanks!"\d\ to shut down CurryMUD with a custom message.4`

\u\SEE ALSO\n\
